data.description: Newer Home Built in 2021!  Beautifully constructed 3-bedroom 2 bath 2 car garage home with front porch and covered lanai.  This home offers a split floor plan, tray ceilings in living area and master suite and tile flooring throughout.  Kitchen features include an island counter and soft close cabinets, pure white granite counter tops and window sills to match, pantry and stainless-steel appliances.  Spacious Master Suite provides a large beautiful tiled walk-in shower with glass enclosure and walk in closet with shelving.  Situated on oversized lot and privacy fence needs some work on fence from hurricane.  Also includes security camera system and window treatments.  This home is a must see!  Call to schedule a showing today.
